.row
  .span9
    %h2 Riddle Me There Service
.row
  .span9
    %p 
      All request should include your auth key as a parameter. Either in the URL or in the form with the name: 
      %span.highlight auth_key

    %p 
      You can obtain an authencation key by visiting this page: 
      %a{href:'/create_key'}Create A Key
.row
  .span9
    %h3 Creating a Riddle
    %p
      %h5 Verb
      %span.highlight POST
    %p
      %h5 URL
      %input.span6{type:'text', value: "http://aitp-contest.herokuapp.com/create_riddle"}
    %p
      %h5 Accepts Header
      %span.highlight application/json
      or
      %span.highlight application/xml
    %p
      %h5 Parameters
      %dl
        %dt riddle (string)
        %dd The text that makes up the riddle.
        %dt latitude (decimal)
        %dd A decimal value representing the latitude of the location.
        %dt longitude (decimal)
        %dd A decimal value representing the longitude of the location.
        %dt username (string)
        %dd The username representing the user.
    %p
      %h5 Example Response (applicaiton/json)
      %pre.prettyprint.lang-js
        :preserve
          {
            "id":"5074c7d399151b0cbe000003",
            "latitude":30.20827,
            "longitude":-92.013116,
            "riddle":"Where is this?"
          }
.row
  .span9
    %h3 Local Riddles
    %p
      Finds all riddles within 10 miles of the user.
    %p
      %h5 Verb
      %span.highlight GET
    %p
      %h5 URL
      %input.span6{type:'text', value: "http://aitp-contest.herokuapp.com/local_riddles"}
    %p
      %h5 Accepts Header
      %span.highlight application/json
      or
      %span.highlight application/xml
    %p
      %h5 Parameters
      %dl
        %dt latitude (decimal)
        %dd A decimal value representing the latitude of the current location.
        %dt longitude (decimal)
        %dd A decimal value representing the longitude of the current location.
    %p
      %h5 Example Response (applicaiton/json)
      %pre.prettyprint.lang-js
        :preserve
          [
            {
              "id":"5070688499151b097a000003",
              "latitude":30.20827,
              "longitude":-92.013116,
              "riddle":"Where is this?"
            }
          ]
.row
  .span9
    %h3 Submit Answer
    %p
      Returns 404 if the answer is incorrect, otherwise returns a 200.
    %p
      %h5 Verb
      %span.highlight POST
    %p
      %h5 URL
      %input.span6{type:'text', value: "http://aitp-contest.herokuapp.com/answer"}
    %p
      %h5 Accepts Header
      %span.highlight application/json
      or
      %span.highlight application/xml
    %p
      %h5 Parameters
      %dl
        %dt riddle_id (string)
        %dd The id of the riddle the user is attempting to answer.
        %dt latitude (decimal)
        %dd A decimal value representing the latitude of the current location.
        %dt longitude (decimal)
        %dd A decimal value representing the longitude of the current location.
        %dt username (string)
        %dd The username of the user attempting to answer the riddle.

.row
